0V7a5 5 0 0 1 10 0v3\"></path></svg>Dashboard</a></div></nav></header><main><section class=\"mx-auto grid min-h-[calc(100vh-82px)] max-w-7xl items-center gap-10 px-5 py-12 lg:grid-cols-[0.95fr_1.05fr] lg:py-16\"><div class=\"max-w-3xl\"><div class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-md border border-ink/10 bg-white/80 px-3 py-2 text-sm font-semibold text-ink/75 shadow-sm\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-sparkles text-clay\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M9.937 15.5A2 2 0 0 0 8.5 14.063l-6.135-1.582a.5.5 0 0 1 0-.962L8.5 9.936A2 2 0 0 0 9.937 8.5l1.582-6.135a.5.5 0 0 1 .963 0L14.063 8.5A2 2 0 0 0 15.5 9.937l6.135 1.581a.5.5 0 0 1 0 .964L15.5 14.063a2 2 0 0 0-1.437 1.437l-1.582 6.135a.5.5 0 0 1-.963 0z\"></path><path d=\"M20 3v4\"></path><path d=\"M22 5h-4\"></path><path d=\"M4 17v2\"></path><path d=\"M5 18H3\"></path></svg>Madison, Wisconsin</div><h1 class=\"mt-6 text-5xl font-semibold leading-[0.94] tracking-tight text-ink sm:text-7xl\">A personal website with a private command center.</h1><p class=\"mt-6 max-w-2xl text-xl leading-8 text-ink/72\">Operator, builder, and systems-minded problem solver</p><p class=\"mt-5 max-w-2xl text-base leading-7 text-ink/65\">A clean personal hub for professional presence, life systems, documents, planning, and the resources that keep each week moving.</p><div class=\"mt-8 flex flex-wrap gap-3\"><a class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-md bg-ink px-5 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-paper shadow-crisp transition hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:bg-moss\" href=\"/resume\">View Resume<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"17\" height=\"17\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></a><a class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-md border border-ink/15 bg-white/75 px-5 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-ink shadow-sm transition hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:bg-white\" href=\"/dashboard\">Open Dashboard</a></div></div><div class=\"surface overflow-hidden rounded-lg p-3\"><div class=\"relative aspect-[4/3] overflow-hidden rounded-md bg-mist\"><img alt=\"A polished desk workspace with documents, notebook, and dashboard screen\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" class=\"object-cover\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\" sizes=\"(min-width: 1024px) 50vw, 100vw\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fhero-workspace.png&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fhero-workspace.png&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fhero-workspace.png&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fhero-workspace.png&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fhero-workspace.png&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fhero-workspace.png&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fhero-workspace.png&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fhero-workspace.png&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fhero-workspace.png&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fhero-workspace.png&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\"/></div><div class=\"grid gap-3 p-3 sm:grid-cols-3\"><div class=\"rounded-md bg-paper p-4\"><p class=\"text-2xl font-semibold text-ink\">4</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.12em] text-ink/45\">Public pages</p></div><div class=\"rounded-md bg-paper p-4\"><p class=\"text-2xl font-semibold text-ink\">10</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.12em] text-ink/45\">Private modules</p></div><div class=\"rounded-md bg-paper p-4\"><p class=\"text-2xl font-semibold text-ink\">2</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.12em] text-ink/45\">Customizable files</p></div></div></div></section><section class=\"border-y border-ink/10 bg-white/55\"><div class=\"mx-auto grid max-w-7xl gap-4 px-5 py-10 md:grid-cols-3\"><article class=\"rounded-lg border border-ink/10 bg-paper p-6 shadow-sm\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"26\" height=\"26\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-sparkles text-clay\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M9.937 15.5A2 2 0 0 0 8.5 14.063l-6.135-1.582a.5.5 0 0 1 0-.962L8.5 9.936A2 2 0 0 0 9.937 8.5l1.582-6.135a.5.5 0 0 1 .963 0L14.063 8.5A2 2 0 0 0 15.5 9.937l6.135 1.581a.5.5 0 0 1 0 .964L15.5 14.063a2 2 0 0 0-1.437 1.437l-1.582 6.135a.5.5 0 0 1-.963 0z\"></path><path d=\"M20 3v4\"></path><path d=\"M22 5h-4\"></path><path d=\"M4 17v2\"></path><path d=\"M5 18H3\"></path></svg><h2 class=\"mt-5 text-xl font-semibold text-ink\">Public presence</h2><p class=\"mt-3 text-sm leading-6 text-ink/65\">A simple home for your background, resume, contact details, and professional signal.</p></article><article class=\"rounded-lg border border-ink/10 bg-paper p-6 shadow-sm\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"26\" height=\"26\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-layout-dashboard text-clay\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><rect width=\"7\" height=\"9\" x=\"3\" y=\"3\" rx=\"1\"></rect><rect width=\"7\" height=\"5\" x=\"14\" y=\"3\" rx=\"1\"></rect><rect width=\"7\" height=\"9\" x=\"14\" y=\"12\" rx=\"1\"></rect><rect width=\"7\" height=\"5\" x=\"3\" y=\"16\" rx=\"1\"></rect></svg><h2 class=\"mt-5 text-xl font-semibold text-ink\">Private operating system</h2><p class=\"mt-3 text-sm leading-6 text-ink/65\">A protected dashboard for the everyday references, plans, and routines that keep life moving.</p></article><article class=\"rounded-lg border border-ink/10 bg-paper p-6 shadow-sm\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"26\" height=\"26\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-shield-check text-clay\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 13c0 5-3.5 7.5-7.66 8.95a1 1 0 0 1-.67-.01C7.5 20.5 4 18 4 13V6a1 1 0 0 1 1-1c2 0 4.5-1.2 6.24-2.72a1.17 1.17 0 0 1 1.52 0C14.51 3.81 17 5 19 5a1 1 0 0 1 1 1z\"></path><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg><h2 class=\"mt-5 text-xl font-semibold text-ink\">Deployment ready</h2><p class=\"mt-3 text-sm leading-6 text-ink/65\">Environment-based password settings and Cloudflare deployment notes are included.</p></article></div></section><section class=\"mx-auto grid max-w-7xl gap-8 px-5 py-12 lg:grid-cols-[0.8fr_1.2fr]\"><div><p class=\"text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.16em] text-cobalt\">Built for everyday use</p><h2 class=\"mt-4 text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-ink sm:text-5xl\">Public signal up front. Private systems behind the lock.</h2></div><div class=\"grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2\"><article class=\"surface rounded-lg p-6\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-file-text text-cobalt\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M15 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V7Z\"></path><path d=\"M14 2v4a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h4\"></path><path d=\"M10 9H8\"></path><path d=\"M16 13H8\"></path><path d=\"M16 17H8\"></path></svg><h3 class=\"mt-5 text-xl font-semibold text-ink\">Professional base</h3><p class=\"mt-3 text-sm leading-6 text-ink/65\">About, resume, contact, and profile links are ready for your real details.</p></article><article class=\"surface rounded-lg p-6\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-calendar-check text-cobalt\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M8 2v4\"></path><path d=\"M16 2v4\"></path><rect width=\"18\" height=\"18\" x=\"3\" y=\"4\" rx=\"2\"></rect><path d=\"M3 10h18\"></path><path d=\"m9 16 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg><h3 class=\"mt-5 text-xl font-semibold text-ink\">Personal operations</h3><p class=\"mt-3 text-sm leading-6 text-ink/65\">Calendar, tasks, travel, documents, wedding, home, and work resources live together.</p></article></div></section></main><!--$--><!--/$--><footer class=\"border-t border-ink/10 bg-ink text-paper\"><div class=\"mx-auto grid max-w-7xl gap-8 px-5 py-10 text-sm sm:grid-cols-[1fr_auto] sm:items-end\"><div><p class=\"text-lg font-semibold\">Matthew Schuppel</p><p class=\"mt-2 max-w-xl text-paper/65\">A clean personal hub for professional presence, life systems, documents, planning, and the resources that keep each week moving.</p></div><div class=\"space-y-2 text-paper/70 sm:text-right\"><p>yourdomain.com</p><p>© <!-- -->2026<!-- --> All rights reserved.</p></div></div></footer><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/webpack-d0d7fc50fd05f285.js\" id=\"_R_\" async=\"\"></script><script>(self.__next_f=self.__next_f||[]).push([0])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,\"1:\\\"$Sreact.fragment\\\"\\n2:I[8898,[\\\"898\\\",\\\"static/chunks/898-dd3a73578fffcbfe.js\\\",\\\"151\\\",\\\"static/chunks/151-ba81253e12657fd6.js\\\",\\\"974\\\",\\\"static/chunks/app/page-02189c9411577ad4.js\\\"],\\\"\\\"]\\n3:I[4827,[],\\\"\\\"]\\n4:I[1063,[],\\\"\\\"]\\n9:I[6177,[],\\\"\\\"]\\n:HL[\\\"/_next/static/css/520715de609ad9dc.css\\\",\\\"style\\\"]\\n\"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,\"0:{\\\"P\\\":null,\\\"b\\\":\\\"TagSeXkZksrR1-R7Y7R6Y\\\",\\\"p\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"c\\\":[\\\"\\\",\\\"\\\"],\\\"i\\\":false,\\\"f\\\":[[[\\\"\\\",{\\\"children\\\":[